00:41:35.457 --> 00:41:37.096
Ganun ba talaga kahalaga ang jade na 'yan?

00:41:38.777 --> 00:41:39.817
Siyempre naman.

00:41:40.536 --> 00:41:42.056
Ito ang huling kayamanan

00:41:42.056 --> 00:41:44.136
